'''Gamorrean''', known disparagingly as "'''pig'''," was a [[language]] spoken by the [[Gamorrean]] [[species]]. [[Human]]s could learn it, as [[Alys Ongwa]] did during the [[High Republic Era]].<ref name="Midnight Horizon" />

